            "style": "",
            "text": " and private sales, however the 1937 Bugatti Type 57S Sports Tourer slated for Bonhams’ Amelia Island Auction is really turning heads. Estimated to auction for between $10,000,000 and $12,000,000 this obviously is a standout even among blue-chip pre-war cars.",
